Six people are reported dead and 25 injured after a head-on collision between a bus and a taxi on the D2940 road near Tonga in KwaDladla, Mpumalanga. Spokesperson for the Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison Joseph Mabuza says the injured have been taken to nearby hospitals. <a href="https://iono.fm/e/598212">Content hosted by iono.fm</a>